{"tid":55423,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"波蘭zakopane之旅","createTime":"2016-12-26T11:34:14.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-30T16:52:51.000Z","uid":17247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7c1d4e29b14a6686841834ac0cb504ca0fa61e0b","tid":55423,"uid":17247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T11:34:14.000Z","msg":"搭完十一個鐘巴士，柏林到zakopane, 依加到左bnb,一陣出去搵食<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/49222px.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F49222px.jpg&h=0c2cd903&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea59762f7530e094251b64f1b2543eaa2794ce2a","tid":55423,"uid":23751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T11:54:37.000Z","msg":"我都諗住17年去ZAKOPANE順便行下山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd1bcd9a7183b59fa1d6ddfa66e8b27ba7dd98f6","tid":55423,"uid":66954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T12:21:06.000Z","msg":"小販檔d膠筋芝士，以為自己食緊膠<br />\n<br />\nbtw morskie oko必去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知結咗冰未呢"},{"pid":"db55c175a36f44234a6bbaf9075a044c290368c1","tid":55423,"uid":17247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T17:18:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小販檔d膠筋芝士，以為自己食緊膠<br />\n<br />\nbtw morskie oko必去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知結咗冰未呢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講起呢舊野，其實點食，買完係街一野咬落去，之後完全咬唔入，就好柒咁放返入袋... <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/27/011822_293096f8d82c8847872f9bfd7d274666.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F27%2F011822_293096f8d82c8847872f9bfd7d274666.jpg&h=2ec9232f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"16a03fd45b66c638c9b0b67476fdffe670f9d256","tid":55423,"uid":17247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T17:31:55.000Z","msg":"Nosal skiing/snowboarding site, 聽聞係最新手lvl 既滑雪場，聽日打算挑戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54776c5261ec724e0f579b822c8a5aabacdd270e","tid":55423,"uid":17247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T17:32:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Nosal skiing/snowboarding site, 聽聞係最新手lvl 既滑雪場，聽日打算挑戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"77706c85e42cb4cd77d2642cd4ab3c661e327d53","tid":55423,"uid":17247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T17:33:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Nosal skiing/snowboarding site, 聽聞係最新手lvl 既滑雪場，聽日打算挑戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8g3g7KW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8g3g7KW.jpg&h=2de2ab57&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4036a12276e1f5698c7388d1c55bbb4a61fd99de","tid":55423,"uid":17247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T17:35:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LFAUTEP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLFAUTEP.jpg&h=f0698537&s={SIZE}\" /> 波蘭佬既搭棚，好似好唔穩陣"},{"pid":"04775c776ea21b06b16f08be8835d548e0aca63e","tid":55423,"uid":35372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T17:37:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小販檔d膠筋芝士，以為自己食緊膠<br />\n<br />\nbtw morskie oko必去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知結咗冰未呢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講起呢舊野，其實點食，買完係街一野咬落去，之後完全咬唔入，就好柒咁放返入袋... <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/27/011822_293096f8d82c8847872f9bfd7d274666.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F27%2F011822_293096f8d82c8847872f9bfd7d274666.jpg&h=2ec9232f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌我月頭去左 呢舊野又係食左兩啖dum左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我乜gear都無去左moski oko之後上多百幾米去另一個湖 果段路就真係成呎厚雪啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4830aa98842f827aa8195a89eccaaf12e6c27206","tid":55423,"uid":17247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T17:38:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vs2640z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvs2640z.jpg&h=0a591a6d&s={SIZE}\" /> 山下有條水"},{"pid":"ccae46615d8dab477d12177cc28c070407f4c2ae","tid":55423,"uid":17247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T17:45:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小販檔d膠筋芝士，以為自己食緊膠<br />\n<br />\nbtw morskie oko必去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知結咗冰未呢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講起呢舊野，其實點食，買完係街一野咬落去，之後完全咬唔入，就好柒咁放返入袋... <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/27/011822_293096f8d82c8847872f9bfd7d274666.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F27%2F011822_293096f8d82c8847872f9bfd7d274666.jpg&h=2ec9232f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌我月頭去左 呢舊野又係食左兩啖dum左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我乜gear都無去左moski oko之後上多百幾米去另一個湖 果段路就真係成呎厚雪啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個我都想去。睇相好靚，但怕自己d gear 唔夠，得件羽絨 夜晚已經凍，同著對dr martens 應該會仆死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a0f723a22506e9c5ae2ff2c793b553582f604c6","tid":55423,"uid":17247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T17:47:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O37WpQC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO37WpQC.jpg&h=fd6674b1&s={SIZE}\" /> 有馬車係街行勁慢頂住條路，但d 司機又無咩野咁"},{"pid":"a2d748b8ab60cfc325102048df2142b4e7f376fb","tid":55423,"uid":35372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T17:59:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小販檔d膠筋芝士，以為自己食緊膠<br />\n<br />\nbtw morskie oko必去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知結咗冰未呢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講起呢舊野，其實點食，買完係街一野咬落去，之後完全咬唔入，就好柒咁放返入袋... <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/27/011822_293096f8d82c8847872f9bfd7d274666.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F27%2F011822_293096f8d82c8847872f9bfd7d274666.jpg&h=2ec9232f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌我月頭去左 呢舊野又係食左兩啖dum左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我乜gear都無去左moski oko之後上多百幾米去另一個湖 果段路就真係成呎厚雪啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個我都想去。睇相好靚，但怕自己d gear 唔夠，得件羽絨 夜晚已經凍，同著對dr martens 應該會仆死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nmoski oko車路嚟 唔難去 不過單程要行2個鐘 我上果日-15度 我連羽絨都無 我著nike跑鞋上添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小心跣親就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dd3f94154b19c357a0a2d458fc099556ca8462b","tid":55423,"uid":55956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T18:07:22.000Z","msg":"6月去過 好鍾意呢個地方 morskie oko真係不得了 條路又易行 冬天去應該仲正"},{"pid":"53421168f96e91beba6653fc10acb16586050524","tid":55423,"uid":33363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T01:38:18.000Z","msg":"一月去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲諗緊一日行山一日滑雪定兩日滑雪好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6463a18d39040c2bc1fb0c22796f4a185aeadbb2","tid":55423,"uid":27610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T05:29:27.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"212ee1fb3301d87ae6a31184e8a812a676b86d69","tid":55423,"uid":66954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T10:51:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小販檔d膠筋芝士，以為自己食緊膠<br />\n<br />\nbtw morskie oko必去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知結咗冰未呢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講起呢舊野，其實點食，買完係街一野咬落去，之後完全咬唔入，就好柒咁放返入袋... <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/27/011822_293096f8d82c8847872f9bfd7d274666.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F27%2F011822_293096f8d82c8847872f9bfd7d274666.jpg&h=2ec9232f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌我月頭去左 呢舊野又係食左兩啖dum左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我乜gear都無去左moski oko之後上多百幾米去另一個湖 果段路就真係成呎厚雪啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個我都想去。睇相好靚，但怕自己d gear 唔夠，得件羽絨 夜晚已經凍，同著對dr martens 應該會仆死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nmoski oko車路嚟 唔難去 不過單程要行2個鐘 我上果日-15度 我連羽絨都無 我著nike跑鞋上添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小心跣親就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冬天去過morskie oko真係跣到仆咗幾次街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但無再上另一個湖，見有人行幾步就跣返落黎，d鬼仔同我哋講d雪到佢腰，我去應該沒頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"529be467839eadbd994fdcdb1dc264d4d2247291","tid":55423,"uid":50877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T14:26:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小販檔d膠筋芝士，以為自己食緊膠<br />\n<br />\nbtw morskie oko必去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知結咗冰未呢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講起呢舊野，其實點食，買完係街一野咬落去，之後完全咬唔入，就好柒咁放返入袋... <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/27/011822_293096f8d82c8847872f9bfd7d274666.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F27%2F011822_293096f8d82c8847872f9bfd7d274666.jpg&h=2ec9232f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌我月頭去左 呢舊野又係食左兩啖dum左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我乜gear都無去左moski oko之後上多百幾米去另一個湖 果段路就真係成呎厚雪啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個我都想去。睇相好靚，但怕自己d gear 唔夠，得件羽絨 夜晚已經凍，同著對dr martens 應該會仆死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nmoski oko車路嚟 唔難去 不過單程要行2個鐘 我上果日-15度 我連羽絨都無 我著nike跑鞋上添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小心跣親就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冬天去過morskie oko真係跣到仆咗幾次街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但無再上另一個湖，見有人行幾步就跣返落黎，d鬼仔同我哋講d雪到佢腰，我去應該沒頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n今年6月上過去<br />\n要係上面睇番落morskie oko先靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf00af3a4d8be6218859dbb714a81988b492f7d2","tid":55423,"uid":1666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T15:53:35.000Z","msg":"黎緊會去波蘭，巴打仲去左咩地方，有咩特別野需要注意架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81bbe915f2ad8f45fab831dddee462c73067c7cb","tid":55423,"uid":33752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T16:52:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小販檔d膠筋芝士，以為自己食緊膠<br />\n<br />\nbtw morskie oko必去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知結咗冰未呢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講起呢舊野，其實點食，買完係街一野咬落去，之後完全咬唔入，就好柒咁放返入袋... <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/27/011822_293096f8d82c8847872f9bfd7d274666.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F27%2F011822_293096f8d82c8847872f9bfd7d274666.jpg&h=2ec9232f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢舊係芝士黎架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個陣拎左返屋企切片夾麵包，再係微波爐叮一叮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}